premise_source_doc_sentence: Christine Diane Teigen  (  -LSB- ` tiːgən -RSB- born November 30 , 1985  )  is an American model .
She made her debut in the annual Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue in 2010 and , alongside Nina Agdal and Lily Aldridge , appeared on the cover in 2014 .
She co-hosts Lip Sync Battle with LL Cool J on Spike TV and joined the lifestyle panel talk show FABLife .
The show is hosted by rapper LL Cool J , while model Chrissy Teigen serves as color commentator .

She is a Victoria 's Secret Angel and a Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue model , appearing as a rookie alongside Chrissy Teigen and Nina Agdal in 2014 for the cover of the issue 's 50th anniversary .
